01:00:32,370 --> 01:00:35,630
jeep and go around the island and see the
Wildlife Reserve?"

807
01:00:35,630 --> 01:00:42,290
"Yes, that's it. I love all the animal trips.
I can't wait. Dominic isn't keen at all, but

808
01:00:42,290 --> 01:00:47,460
he says he doesn't mind as long as he gets
his golf, Typical! It's like he's married

809
01:00:47,460 --> 01:00:55,220
to the stupid game. I find it so dull. He
loves it, though. Do you play golf, Eddie?"

810
01:00:55,220 --> 01:00:57,200
